==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: coelogyne
<hw>coelogyne</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>any of various orchids of the
genus <gen>Coelogyne</gen> which may have clusters of fragrant lacy
snow-white flowers; sinister salmon-pink solitary flowers; chainlike
racemes of topaz and chocolate brown flowers; spikes of delicate white
spice-scented flowers; or emerald green flowers marked with
blue-black.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coelospermous</ent>⟦br⟧
